        .. code-block:: pycon

            >>> Quaternion(0, 0, 1, 1) * 2
            Quaternion(0.0, 0.0, 2.0, 2.0)
            >>> Quaternion(0, 1, 0, 1) * Quaternion(1, 2, 3, 0)
            Quaternion(4.0, 2.0, 2.0, -2.0)
